## Pokémon FireRed/LeafGreen Alt Main Golbat

If manipping Squirtle, go for Natures Mild or Rash, and min. IV: Atk x/22/x, Def 7/0/x, Sp.Atk x/x/28, Speed: x/19/x.  
Attack and speed are useful for bridge rival.  
If not manipping Squirtle, want 12 Atk at level 6, 11 Sp.Atk at level 5 (12 at level 6 with +1 on level up), and outspeed Bulbasaur.  
For manipless, change "directinput=true" to "directinput=false" in the first line of the source file.

Before starting your run, make sure your save file has the following:
  - Text: Fast
  - Battle Animations: Off
  - Style: Set
  - Button Mode: L=A

Give yourself a 1 character name  
Head outside then head north towards the grass have Oak stop you  
Mash through text until you can pick Squirtle (middle Pokeball). Give it a one character name
- Optional: check stats here (can skip)

Head down and fight your rival

:::::trainer[Rival 1]
  - Tackle spam
  - After the battle, check your Level 6 stats and enter them into the tracker
:::::

If manipless, put cursor on Bag when leaving lab (skips a cutscene before Route 1)

Grab the Potion from mart guy

Kill at least a Level 3 or a Level 2 on Route 1
- Can kill Level 2 + Level 3 to hit Level 7 (not necessary, but having Bubble for Sammy helps)

Grab the parcel at the mart then head back to Oak’s lab

Catch Rattata/Pidgey if you come across them on the second way up (Tackle/Bubble to weaken)
  - Don’t try to force an encounter since there’s backups later

Head to Viridian Forest

- Skip all the Bugcatchers until Sammy
- Grab the Antidote after the second Bugcatcher (after the sign)
- Grab the hidden Potion next to Sammy

:::::::trainer[Bug Catcher Sammy]
  :::::pokemon[Weedle]
    :::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=13-" level=7}
	  :info[Slower at -0 Speed]{color=red}
	:::
	:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=14" level=7}
      :info[Ties at -0 Speed (at Level 7) - slower at Level 6]{color=yellow}
	:::
    - Swap Tackle to Slot 2
	- Bubble spam (if you don't have Bubble, Tail Whip and Tackle spam)
    - Weedle's Poison Sting always does 3
	- A poison tick does 2 if you have 23 or less Max HP, 3 if you have 24 or more Max HP
  :::::
:::::::

If you got poisoned, Antidote depending on your SpAtk:
:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spa=14" level=8}
- You won't be able to OHKO Geodude, Antidote so Tackle from Geodude puts you into high Torrent for Sandshrew (usually around 12-14HP)
:::
:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spa=15+" level=8}
- Antidote at 7/25, 6/26 or 7/27 HP (to keep Torrent for Sandshrew)
- Can go to 5 or 6 HP if you get Level 12 for Onix or can OHKO it at Level 11 (28+ SpAtk Modest/Mild/Rash)
:::

Head to the gym, fight the minion

:::::::trainer[Camper Liam]
  :::::pokemon[Geodude]
    - Bubble (x2)
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble*]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=8 opponentStat=11 healthThreshold=28 special=true stab=true torrent=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Geodude's Tackle]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=8 opponentLevel=10 opponentStat=21 special=false stab=false}
  :::::
  :::::pokemon[Sandshrew]
	:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spa=15-" level=9}
      - Bubble x3
	:::
	:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spa=16+" level=9}
      - Bubble* x2 (75% to 2HKO in Torrent)
	:::
    ::damage[Sandshrew's Scratch]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=40 level=9 opponentLevel=11 opponentStat=21 special=false stab=false}
  :::::
:::::::

:::::::trainer[Leader Brock]
  :::::pokemon[Geodude]
    Bubble (x2)
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble* (at Level 10)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=10 opponentStat=12 healthThreshold=31 special=true stab=true torrent=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble (at Level 11)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=11 opponentStat=12 healthThreshold=31 special=true stab=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble* (at Level 11)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=11 opponentStat=12 healthThreshold=31 special=true stab=true torrent=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Geodude's Tackle (at Level 10)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=10 opponentLevel=12 opponentStat=24 special=false stab=false}
    ::damage[Geodude's Tackle (at Level 10 - after using Withdraw)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=10 combatStages=1 opponentLevel=12 opponentStat=24 special=false stab=false}
    ::damage[Geodude's Tackle (at Level 11)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=11 opponentLevel=12 opponentStat=24 special=false stab=false}
    ::damage[Geodude's Tackle (at Level 11 - after using Withdraw)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=11 combatStages=1 opponentLevel=12 opponentStat=24 special=false stab=false}
  :::::
  :::::pokemon[Onix]
	:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=15-" level=11}
      :info[Slower than Onix after a Bubble speedfall]{color=red}
	:::
	:::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=16" level=11}
      :info[Tied with Onix after a Bubble speedfall]{color=yellow}
	:::
    :::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=17+" level=11}
	  :info[Faster than Onix after a Bubble speedfall]{color=green}
    :::
    - Bubble (x2)
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble*]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=11 opponentStat=18 healthThreshold=33 special=true stab=true torrent=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Chance to OHKO with Bubble* (at Level 12)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=true movePower=20 level=12 opponentStat=18 healthThreshold=33 special=true stab=true torrent=true effectiveness=4}
    ::damage[Onix's Tackle]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=11 opponentLevel=14 opponentStat=17 special=false}
    ::damage[Onix's Tackle (after using Withdraw)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=35 level=11 combatStages=1 opponentLevel=14 opponentStat=17 special=false}
    ::damage[Onix's Rock Tomb]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=50 level=11 opponentLevel=14 opponentStat=17 special=false stab=true}
    ::damage[Onix's Rock Tomb (after using Withdraw)]{source="Squirtle" offensive=false movePower=50 level=11 combatStages=1 opponentLevel=14 opponentStat=17 special=false stab=true}
  :::::
  - Teach WG over Tail Whip (Slot 1)
:::::::

After leaving the gym, enter the Mart

:::card
Sell: Rock Tomb

Buy:
- 9 Potions (10 if 2 Antidotes or 0 Para Heal)
- 3 Antidotes (can buy 2 if still have one)
- 1 Parlyz Heal (if no cutter yet)
- 3 Awakenings
- 1 Escape Rope
- 4 Repels
:::

Head to Route 3 to get your running shoes

:::::::trainer[Bug Catcher Colton]
  - Try to end up at an HP after this fight where you keep Torrent for at least Level 14
  :::::pokemon[Caterpie]
    :::if{source="Squirtle" condition="spe=20-" level=13}
